metadata.name: Hrafn Larsson
metadata.description: A mighty and burly champion of the Guild of Thor, this viking has spent his entire life training for war. Now that it is finally here, he is as ready as ever for combat. But tread carefully, oh mighty viking, for only a fool overestimates his own powers, and a fool is sure to fall when the Midgard does too. Welcome to the end of the world. Welcome to Ragnarok.
